            | report_declaration_agreedBehalfDeputy_2 | more_deputies_not_behalf |
            | report_declaration_agreedBehalfDeputyExplanation |  |
        And I press "report_declaration_save"
        Then the following fields should have an error:
            | report_declaration_agreedBehalfDeputyExplanation |
